.callout
  %strong Finished calculation! Your Twitter account is worth
  %h1 $0.00
  %strong
    Rating:
    = rating_insult

Here are the calculations Tweetsworth used:

%table.data
  %tr
    %td
      %img{:src => "/tweets.gif"}
      %h3
        Total Tweets:
        %strong= @person.statuses_count
      = tweet_insult(@person.statuses_count)
    %td
      %img{:src => "/globe.gif"}
      %h3
        Followers:
        %strong= @person.followers_count
      = follower_insult(@person.followers_count)
  %tr
    %td
      %img{:src => "/member.gif"}
      %h3
        Tweeting Since:
        %strong= @person.joined_twitter_at.strftime("%B %d %Y")
      = duration_insult(@person.joined_twitter_at)
    %td
      %img{:src => "/retweet.gif"}
      %h3
        Retweets:
        %strong Unknown.
      = retweet_insult